# Evidence (temporary)

reinguard is bootstrapping. **Structured GitHub / git observation** will live in
`rgd` (see ADRs **ADR-0003**, **ADR-0006**).

Until `rgd observe` and related commands exist in this repository:

- Agents **may** use the **`gh` CLI** and **`git`** directly for read-only
  inspection when implementing or reviewing GitHub workflows.
- Prefer capturing stable behavior in **tests** and **CI** rather than ad-hoc
  scripts.

This file will be deleted or replaced when observation is fully implemented in
`rgd`.
